Class.name: Custom.SWARH.HIPS.ws.v1.q3.LocalClinicalDocumentMetaData
Class.Description: <summary> This object is used for individual local document meta-data items from the local document store </summary> Created from: http://sahipsh00.swarh.net:50500/HIPSServer_TEST/HIPS.Service.PCEHRService.svc?xsd=xsd5

Property.name: AdmissionDate
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the date and time of admission for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: AdmissionReason
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the admission reason for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: DischargeDate
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the date and time of discharge for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: DocumentType
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the type of the document. </summary>

Property.name: ResponsibleProviderFamilyName
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the family name of the patient's responsible provider for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: ResponsibleProviderGivenNames
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the given names of the patient's responsible provider for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: ResponsibleProviderSuffix
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the suffix of the patient's responsible provider (such as 'Jr' or 'Sr') for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: ResponsibleProviderTitle
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the title of the patient's responsible provider (such as 'Dr', 'Ms' or 'Mr') for the episode that this document relates to. </summary>

Property.name: SourceSystemDocumentId
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the Document ID of the document version. </summary>

Property.name: SourceSystemSetId
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the Set ID of the document, which is common to all versions of the document. </summary>

Property.name: Status
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the status of the document within the local repository. </summary>

Property.name: SupersededDate
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the date and time when this document version was superseded by a newer version uploaded to the PCEHR system. </summary>

Property.name: UploadedDate
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the date and time when this document version was uploaded to the PCEHR system. </summary>
